If you have to place everything for sale in a Trader's Satchel, how would you sell containers?  Many tailors are selling handmade containers like backpacks and sacks - how do you put those in a Trader's Satchel?  Or Rallic Packs?  I make/sell Rallic Packs all the time for a little extra cash...<BR>
<BR>
Also, like MANY people I know, I've been using Trader's Satchels in my bank ever since I got Luclin in order to increase my Bank capacity.  Will the new Bazaar effect that in any way?  If I become a /vendor ... will that put everything in my Bank that I have in a Trader's Satchel up for sale, or only the items I specify?<BR>
<BR>
If anyone knows of a place with the answers to these questions, or gets a chance to play around with this feature on Test, please post what you learn.  Thanks.<BR>
